apoor\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/news/ni59031645/|title=Kanika Kapoor launches her first single titled 'The Teddy Bear Song'|publisher=[[IMDb]]|accessdate=31 January 2016|date=22 September 2015|author=bollyspice.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Main Aur Charles]]''\n| \"Jab Chaye Tera Jadoo\"\n| Sanjeev-Darshan\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/music/news/Jab-Chhaye-Mera-Jadoo-recreated-for-Main-Aur-Charles/articleshow/49336975.cms|title='Jab Chhaye Mera Jadoo' recreated for 'Main Aur Charles'|work=[[The Times of India]]|accessdate=14 October 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Hate Story 3]]''\n| \"Neendein Khul Jaati Hain\"\n| Meet Bros\n|<ref name=\"youtube.com\"/>\n|-\n| ''Super Girl From China''\n| \"Super Girl From China\"\n| Kanika Kapoor\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/super-girl-from-china-feat./id1064405451?ign-mpt=uo%3D8|title=Super Girl From China (feat. Kanika Kapoor) \u2013 Single by Mika Singh on iTunes|publisher=[[iTunes Store]]|date=3 December 2015|accessdate=5 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Dilwale (2015 film)|Dilwale]]''\n| \"Premika\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Pritam]] Chakraborty\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/in/album/dilwale-original-motion-picture/id1057567669|title=Dilwale (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) by Pritam on iTunes|publisher=[[iTunes Store]]|accessdate=3 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| \"Tukur Tukur\"\n|<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report-watch-new-song-tukur-tukur-from-dilwale-will-make-you-groove-on-the-dance-floor-2155485|title=Watch: New song 'Tukur Tukur' from 'Dilwale' will make you groove on the dance floor!|work=[[DNA India]]|date=14 December 2015|accessdate=16 December 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"11\"|2016\n| ''[[Kyaa Kool Hain Hum 3]]''\n| \"Jawaani Le Doobi\"\n| [[Sajid\u2013Wajid]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/jawaani-le-doobi-from-kyaa/id1069286831|title=Jawaani Le Doobi (Fro