hra]]''\n| \"Luv Letter\"\n|[[Meet Bros]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/music/news/Watch-Aditi-Rao-Hydaris-peppy-Love-letter/articleshow/53264961.cms|title=Watch: Aditi Rao Hydari's peppy 'Love letter'|work=The Times of India|author=Kaushal, Ruchi|accessdate=18 July 2016|date=18 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[A Flying Jatt]]''\n| \"Beat Pe Booty\n| [[Sachin-Jigar]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.saavn.com/s/album/hindi/A-Flying-Jatt-2016/slORX8XBpsA_|title=A Flying Jatt Album at Saavn|work=[[Saavn]]|date=21 July 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Jaguar (2016 film)|Jaguar]]'' <small>(Kannada)</small>\n| \"Selfie\"\n| [[S. S. Thaman]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/in/album/jaguar-original-motion-picture/id1150410756|title=Jaguar (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack) \u2013 EP by Thaman S. on iTunes|publisher=[[iTunes Store]]|date=2 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Rokto]]'' (Bengali film)\n| \"Dana Kata Pori\"\n|[[Akassh]]\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Devi (2016 film)|Tutak Tutak Tutiya]]''\n| \"Tutak Tutak Tutiya\" </small>(Title Song)</small>\n| Raaj Ashoo\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=youZxz4p8nQ|title=Tutak Tutak Tuitya Audio Jukebox \u2013 T-Series|work=\u2014via T-Series YouTube Channel|date=19 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|2017\n| ''[[Munna Michael]]''\n| \"Shake Karaan\"\n| style=\"text-align:center\" |Meet Bros\n|\n|-\n| ''Resham Da Rumaal''\n| \"Resham Da Rumaal\"\n| Band of Brothers\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ym3lZtbwbEw|title=Resham Da Rumaal Video Song: T-Series|work=\u2014via YouTube|date=25 June 2017|accessdate=26 June 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Tera Intezaar]]''\n| ''Abhagi Piya Ki''\n| Raaj Aashoo\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\" |2018\n|[[Ba Baa Black Sheep|Babaablacksheep]]\n|Galla Goriyaa/Aaja Soniye\n|\n|\n|-\n|Nachdi Firangi\n|\"Nachdi Firangi\"\n|Meet bros\n|\n|-\n|Pretty Girl\n|\"Pretty Girl\"\n|\n|\n|-\n|Cheater Mohan\n|\"Cheater Mohan\"\n|\n|\n|-\n|Tha